{"tid":593707,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微信朋友圈推銷投資項目 2,000人疑墮騙局涉10億港元","createTime":"2018-03-15T08:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T10:29:01.000Z","uid":10958,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"48f5f233e5713c8c6cefce57d5fc45be44ec850f","tid":593707,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:15:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>微信朋友圈推銷投資項目 2,000人疑墮騙局涉10億港元</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180313&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57941950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180313%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57941950&d=TJ3MZuC4%2BvlQOXGaWtZ5AUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=a6f15cc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180313%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57941950&h=35517c27\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180313&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57941950</a><br />\n<br />\n繼日前有數十名台灣人懷疑墮入本港倫敦金騙局，近日亦有港人報稱捲入無牌投資騙案。十多名市民報稱在在過去數年曾參與「馬勝金融」的投資項目，原以為每月可提供6%至8%回報。惟「馬勝金融」於2015年被證監會揭發進行無牌投資，資金全部被凍結。苦主料多達2,000名港人，涉及金額高達10億港元。<br />\n<br />\n11名苦主今召開記者會申訴，苦主劉小姐表示，2014年透過朋友在微信朋友圈發帖，得知「馬勝金融」的投資項目。她稱，當時被告之該公司從事外匯、黃金、金礦、沉香、香蕉園、酒店等項目，她更曾自費到新加坡視察投資項目。<br />\n<br />\n劉小姐指，由於有關投資產品聲稱「保本」，她個人便購買7個投資單位。不過，「馬勝金融」於2015年爆煲後，劉小姐被要求將涉投資項目金額轉為公司股票，公司更聲稱將於2016年上市，有關股票亦要存入指定信託公司。但事件至今，該公司未作任何上市，她亦懷疑有關資產被轉移，她和其他苦主未能成功取回本金，她個人則損失約150萬元。<br />\n劉小姐稱，去年10月有關公司代表一度在澳門與苦主見面，聲稱會在馬來西亞賣地，所得金額將賠予苦主們，要求給予3個月時間，但至今未有進度，故決定在本周內報警求助。<br />\n協助苦主的民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸指，有關投資產品未獲證監會批准，但涉事人至今仍可逍遙法外，形容事件「仲慘過雷曼」。她又指，台灣、南韓、新加坡等地涉案者已相繼落網，但香港當局未有行動，「仲話亞洲金融中心，你變咗亞洲金融犯罪中心。」她已促請保安局盡快調查事件，稍後會協助苦主報警。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180313/large/1520939262_f4e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F1520939262_f4e8.jpg&h=199fdc15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180313/large/1520939264_ac84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F1520939264_ac84.jpg&h=1f3b3814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180313/large/1520939267_12a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180313%2Flarge%2F1520939267_12a5.jpg&h=9ec2933b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180313/57941950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F57941950&d=TJ3MZuC4%2BvlQOXGaWtZ5AUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=4192fbf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180313%2F57941950&h=72e4db9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180313/57941950</a>"},{"pid":"203ae618d8d3466876cab144d64349ee72d6d982","tid":593707,"uid":93266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"除左讚好 , 鼓掌 , 歡喜之外<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知講咩好"},{"pid":"cae949ea873e2dbd292c9dec6179ca78bf8e9001","tid":593707,"uid":164799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ebd24bb4972cebc4d3eab98bc8a4506ec9e1b2","tid":593707,"uid":96486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:18:33.000Z","msg":"成日都諗，騙案既受害者有能力賺到咁多錢，但點解連少少既分析能力都冇"},{"pid":"a4fa70bfaeeed13b48c926cb745551d33e185494","tid":593707,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T08:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi